---
title: Carb Smart Sesame-Crusted Chicken Thigh Salad with Avocado and Creamy Sesame Dressing
description: Juicy seared chicken, coated in sesame seeds, sits on top fresh spinach, avocado and tomato salad. But the best part of this tasty dish is the nutty, craveable sesame dressing!
